Class CouponDBDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • dao.CouponDBDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CouponDAO

    public class CouponDBDAO
extends java.lang.Object
implements CouponDAO
    the CouponDBDAO hold all of the methods that are responsible for the coupons's actions. the methods can be used by all of the clients, according to their authorization. these methods connect to the database and retrieves data for the user or write data received from the user to the database
